635
01:15:12.319 --> 01:15:14.857
Lucien.

636
01:15:37.553 --> 01:15:38.752
Oh, fuck.

637
01:16:03.913 --> 01:16:06.321
Help me. Please, help me.

638
01:16:06.457 --> 01:16:08.497
No, no, no, no, no, no, no.

639
01:16:55.507 --> 01:16:58.841
Don't... don't let them bury me.

640
01:16:59.595 --> 01:17:02.086
I'm not dead.

641
01:17:16.529 --> 01:17:19.530
Anything? Pressure? Pulse?

642
01:17:19.658 --> 01:17:21.697
Nothing.

643
01:17:24.996 --> 01:17:27.119
We've lost him.

644
01:17:30.251 --> 01:17:32.540
Write the time on the tag.

645
01:17:33.545 --> 01:17:38.089
