- No need for that, Doctor.


646
01:17:38.217 --> 01:17:40.922
I've made all the arrangements.

647
01:17:43.181 --> 01:17:45.221
Whatever.

648
01:17:47.018 --> 01:17:52.605
He's dead. I trust somebody on your end
will take care of the proper paperwork?


649
01:17:56.695 --> 01:18:00.277
No, no, no. No rest.

650
01:18:01.074 --> 01:18:04.490
You'll see it all. 
You'll feel it.

651
01:18:04.619 --> 01:18:07.574
The cold in the coffin...

652
01:18:07.707 --> 01:18:12.250
it is worse...
much, much worse.


653
01:18:24.348 --> 01:18:28.043
<i>Lucien Celine, the great houngan...</i>

654
01:18:28.044 --> 01:18:30.774
<i>He serves me now, too.</i>

655
01:18:31.689 --> 01:18:35.140
Lucien can't protect you.
I hold him fast!


656
01:18:35.568 --> 01:18:38.652
Lucien will turn
your blood to worms.


657
01:18:38.779 --> 01:18:41.816
<i>Oh, yeah? Do you hear me, blanc?</i>

658
01:18:42.199 --> 01:18:44.737
Her head will be taken
as an offering tonight.


659
01:18:44.869 --> 01:18:47.194
No, wait.

660
01:18:55.838 --> 01:18:58.330
To keep you company.

661
01:19:53.398 --> 01:19:57.016
When you wake up, scream,
Dr Alan. Scream all you want.


662
01:19:57.151 --> 01:19:59.607
There is no escape from the grave.

663
01:20:39.403 --> 01:20:43.021
Ohh! Oh, God.

664
01:20:59.089 --> 01:21:01.712
Here!

665
01:21:02.677 --> 01:21:05.715
Here! Here!

666
01:21:10.100 --> 01:21:12.259
Agh! Agh!

667
01:21:13.187 --> 01:21:14.847
Oh, God.

668
01:21:30.538 --> 01:21:32.578
You're alive.

669
01:21:33.249 --> 01:21:35.289
You're alive.

670
01:21:48.974 --> 01:21:51.181
I know it's bad, the poison.

671
01:21:51.602 --> 01:21:53.974
You see things the
living can't see.


672
01:22:20.506 --> 01:22:23.341
<i>This is WWBC in Miami reporting.</i>

673
01:22:23.509 --> 01:22:25.502
