01:24:02.610 --> 01:24:05.896
<i>Libert√©! Libert√©! Libert√©!</i>

686
01:24:48.282 --> 01:24:50.773
Your soul is mine.

687
01:24:54.538 --> 01:24:59.533
Get up, Dr Alan.
