01:25:59.688 --> 01:26:02.061
- Help me.
- Marielle.


693
01:26:06.320 --> 01:26:08.360
Help me.

694
01:26:11.033 --> 01:26:13.073
Dennis.

695
01:26:14.328 --> 01:26:16.535
