01:27:18.977 --> 01:27:21.302
Argh!

701
01:27:46.798 --> 01:27:48.837
Peytraud?

702
01:28:20.123 --> 01:28:22.162
Peytraud.

703
01:28:23.418 --> 01:28:25.457
Dennis?

704
01:28:46.775 --> 01:28:49.776
Argh!

705
01:28:50.863 --> 01:28:53.188
Argh!

706
01:28:55.159 --> 01:28:57.401
Peytraud.

